      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAINT BREE (6) racing well without winning, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 3rd over 305m at this track beaten 3 lengths (17.91) behind Lenny Limes in a Grade 5 on June 21. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from six starts. Makes plenty of appeal. ENERGY TO BURN (2) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish third, beaten 6 lengths (23.21) at this track in a Other over 400m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to be in the finish again. CADILLAC BELLE (1) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth at this track, but was among the placings at this track three back. Well placed here and can atone this time. HARRY CHANA (8) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
